### 2. Mobile `user_active`

Implemented in:

- `DoneAI/src/services/analytics/unified-analytics.ts`

Current behavior:

- emitted once per identified user per local day
- deduped via AsyncStorage
- survives app restarts
- no longer triggered from auth restore/login
- triggered only from a meaningful-event allowlist
- requires:
  - `shouldTrackEvent(USER_ACTIVE)`
  - `shouldIdentifyUser()`

